Welcome to the UCE Birmingham Faculty of Education
Faculty of Education
Our Courses
The needs of children, schools and colleges are the top priority in the UCE
Birmingham Faculty of Education. Our courses for intending teachers, serving
Services & Support
teachers or those simply interested in education issues cover the entire range of
Birmingham
school phases from infant to continuing education, at every study level from
full-time undergraduate to postgraduate level and PhD.
News & Events
Student Profiles
Our courses are nearly all based at Perry Barr, although students training to
teach have placements all around the West Midlands. In some cases, courses are
held in partnership institutions. Students consistently describe the staff as
friendly, supportive and accessible.
